"ngram\": \"The ceremony's artistic director\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"BFMTVover\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"the segment\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"a reference\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Summer\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"a tribute\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nonetheless, theorganisers issued an apologyfor any offence caused, with spokesperson Anne Descamps saying that \\\"clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group \\u2026 If people have taken any offense we are really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theorganisers\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"any offence\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"any offense\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch confirmed on her Instagram last night (July 29) that she had reported the trolls to the police, posting a statement from her attorney, Audrey Msellati.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1796944157563461e-28, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Roberts\", \"score\": 0.5942768600620989, \"rank\": 0.6827173783861142, \"text\": \"Audrey\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Roberts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audrey_Roberts\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"the trolls\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"the police\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"her attorney\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Msellati said Butch has been \\\"the target of an extremely violent campaign of cyber-harassment and defamation.\\\"\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Msellati\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1335}, {\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"an extremely violent campaign\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"cyber-harassment\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"defamation\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She has been threatened with death, torture and rape, and has also been the target of numerous antisemitic, homophobic, sexist and grossophobic [hatred over her weight] insults,\\\" she continued.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"torture\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"rape\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"sexist\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1566}, {\"ngram\": \"grossophobic\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"her weight] insults\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Barbara Butch condemns this vile hatred directed at her, what she represents and what she stands for.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1736, \