my commitment has always been to make everyone dance, and in my own small way to make a nation on the dancefloor.\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my commitment\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3141}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3174}, {\"ngram\": \"my own small way\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3205}, {\"ngram\": \"a nation\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3222}, {\"ngram\": \"the dancefloor\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through my DJ work and my activism, I have always promoted love and inclusivity - for me, this is what will save the world, even when it's falling apart.\\\"\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my DJ work\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3260}, {\"ngram\": \"my activism\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3305}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusivity\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3321}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3355, \"to\": 3364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued: \\\"Today, however, I am the target of yet another - particularly violent - cyber-harassment.\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3445}, {\"ngram\": \"yet another - particularly violent - cyber-harassment\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although at first I decided not to speak out to let the haters cool down, the messages I receive are increasingly extreme.\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the haters\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3566}, {\"ngram\": \"the messages\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All because I have had the honor of representing my country's diversity through art and music, alongside other artists and performers I admire.\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the honor\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 